snippet.title: Escape from the nuke
snippet.description:
Hittite Games, creator of Car Crash and Real Drive game series, presents you the new update of Escape From The Nuke game. In the game, while trying to escape from the atomic bomb and pass through the portals to the parallel universes, the enemy cars will try to smash your car. The version 2 update out now...

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.HittiteGames.Escapefromthenuke
